" /><meta itemprop="recipeCategory" content="Supper" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Fibre" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Vit C" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Vitamin c" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="3 of 5 a day" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Vegetable stew" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Vegetable soup" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="7-day summer diet plan" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="clean eating" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Natural" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Easy" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Healthy" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Vegetarian" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Soups" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Stews" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Freezable" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Everyday" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Weekend" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Summer" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Light" /></div></div><div class="recipe-header__description" itemprop="description"><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden method__content"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>A cross between a soup and a stew, this healthy French dish is packed with vegetables and beans - perfect as a light lunch. If making ahead it will keep in the fridge for a couple of days.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="recipe-header__bottom"><div class="recipe-header__share service-links__container"><div class="service-links"><div class="service-label">Share:</div><ul class="service-links-primary"><li class="service-links-facebook first"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A//www.bbcgoodfood.com/recipes/summer-pistou&amp;t=Summer%20pistou" title="Share on Facebook" class="service-links-facebook service-links-link" rel="nofollow" data-service-name="Facebook"><i class="font-icon font-icon-facebook-large"></i><span class="service-links-text">Facebook</span></a></li><l