ield-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">We absolutely loved this - we had assumed it was just another vegetable soup, but but we were so impressed. The garlic, Parmesan and basil are amazing. I halved the recipe to just do one lunch but as I had bought a whole bunch of basil I stuck the whole lot in which perhaps added a bit of the punch others had been after. Will be making this again.</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-860171"><a id="comment-860171"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"> <span class="comment__author-picture--no-login"></span></div><div class="comment__author-name"> <span class="username">felicityhm</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 16th Jun, 2015</div> </header><div class="comment__rating-and-report-wrapper"><div class="comment__rating"><div class="rate-widget rate-widget-fivestar clear-block rate-processed"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="on">5.05</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="on"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="comment__text"><div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Both my boyfriend and I had this for for lunch and it was really tasty. I think you could get a bit more punch in there, maybe with a bit of lime juice or something, but a very delicious and filling light, summer soup.</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-859851"